.3568.pdf","abstract":"Given a smooth compact Riemannian manifold $M$ and a Hamiltonian $H$ on the cotangent space $T^*M$, strictly convex and superlinear in the momentum variables, we prove uniqueness of certain ergodic invariant Lagrangian graphs within a given homology or cohomology class. In particular, in the context of quasi-integrable Hamiltonian systems, our result implies global uniqueness of Lagrangian KAM tori with rotation vector $\\rho$. This result extends generically to the $C^0$-closure of KAM tori.","arxiv_id":null,"doi":"10.2422/2036-2145.2009.4.03","journal_title":"undefined"},"created_by":null,"proposed_to":[],"id":null,"created_at":{"$date":"2021-07-27T14:18:29.004Z"},"cited_articles":[{"$binary":"Z/HL2vMpTyiW3YqgNUslgA==","$type":"4"}]},{"_id":{"$oid":"610015b5d112b71809959a3b"},"asset_id":{"$binary":"/9+EjMuqT1WoMlwNAW2kLg==","$type":"4"},"payload":{"title":"COMMUTATORS OF DIFFEOMORPHISMS OF A MANIFOLD WITH CORNERS","authors":["J. Lech"],"date":{"$date":"2007-07-27T00:00:00.000Z"},"pdf_url":"https://doi.org/10.1515/dema-2007-0218","abstract":"Semantic Scholar extracted view of ","arxiv_id":null,"doi":"10.1515/dema-2007-0218","journal_title":"undefined"},"created_by":null,"proposed_to":[],"id":null,"created_at":{"$date":"2021-07-27T14:18:29.063Z"},"cited_articles":[{"$binary":"Z/HL2vMpTyiW3YqgNUslgA==","$type":"4"}]},{"_id":{"$oid":"610015b5d112b71809959a3c"},"asset_id":{"$binary":"gtmP3N/LRGie+fwFHCDfHw==","$type":"4"},"payload":{"title":"Groups of diffeomorphisms and geometric wraps of manifolds over ultra-normed fields","authors":["S. Ludkovsky"],"date":{"$date":"2007-07-27T00:00:00.000Z"},"pdf_url":"https://doi.org/10.1007/s10958-012-0904-2","abstract":"The article is devoted to the study of groups of diffeomorphisms and wraps of manifolds over ultra-metric fields of zero and positive characteristic. Different types of topologies are considered on groups of wraps and diffeomorphisms relative to which they are generalized Lie groups or topol